{"tid":1120433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[CD-ROM請入] 唔使ISP EMAIL 就可以加入連登大家庭！","createTime":"2019-04-22T15:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T17:41:10.000Z","uid":229502,"like":10,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0bae7ffc8c4408b3b8cc7305fdc61c4d85d44924","tid":1120433,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"CD-ROM你好，你係咪好想加入連登？依家有機會喇！最近7-11推出咗連登會員卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會員卡圖例：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tj0H2dz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTj0H2dz.png&h=0a938563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想知道點買呢張會員卡？<br />\n請跟住以下步驟：<br />\n<br />\n1.去你附近嘅7-11 (地鐵站入面嘅最好)<br />\n<br />\n2.入去同店員講「我想買藍精靈，仲有冇貨？」<br />\n<br />\n3.嗰店員會問你「先生/小姐 可唔可以再講多次你要咩？」<br />\n<br />\n最關鍵時刻嚟喇：<br />\n4.你要去拎枝330ml嘅可口可樂，隊去櫃檯嗰度，再講「我仲想要可樂。」<br />\n<br />\n5.嗰店員會拎個對講機話「收到暗號」<br />\n<br />\n6.嗰店員就會拎張卡出嚟畀你，用20蚊就得㗎嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.畀錢再喺連登註冊頁面輸入喺卡後面嘅code (因為個人原因show唔到唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n8.佢會叫你畀一個e-mail account，你是但打一個就得<br />\n<br />\n9.佢會send註冊確認信畀你打咗嘅e-mail account，再跟佢做就<br />\n<br />\n10.完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\